.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, card-games, traveling, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing | card-games | traveling | magic-tricks |

