.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, subway, quad-bike, taxi
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | bus | taxi | subway | quad-bike |

