.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-15::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, fish, dog, frog
1. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the hedgehog##2
3. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
4. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | frog | fish | hedgehog | dog |

